{"tid":1433413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（公審）賤男強姦完未成年少女再打個女仔","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T10:43:55.000Z","uid":225969,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"45d3dc33793f8b4cc6c3627ff3eac68dbcf3300e","tid":1433413,"uid":225969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccqo4PN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fccqo4PN.jpg&h=45a5b434&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ax0THBt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAx0THBt.jpg&h=e0a266ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個賤男ig 係____on99_____  聽人講話咩跟聯和 <br />\n黑社會大曬吖？<br />\n佢強姦完個女仔之後仲要揾人打個女仔，個女仔已經報佐警 有曬證據有曬對話 佢將個賤男做過既野Po曬上ig叫啲女仔小心啲，個賤男就叫佢成班fd網絡欺凌個女仔，原本個女仔Po返成件事岀嚟想澄清返佢唔係自願既，條柒頭就想約個女仔岀嚟傾，個女仔唔肯岀， 個賤男就叫人嚟錄音話知個女仔住邊恐嚇個女仔，個女仔最後冇岀到。<br />\n<br />\n第二日個女仔岀完街返屋企個時 比柒頭啲fd從後拉住個女仔右腳 之後佢成個人跪低 個男人扯住個女仔頭髮 面對面狂打個女仔頭部 打左大約三分鐘冇停過 直到個女仔訓低先收手，之後個女仔攬住佢fd隻腳慢慢起身 然後報警。下面有女仔比人打完之後受傷既相。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qud2A3r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqud2A3r.jpg&h=56e68ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EiHyHJt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEiHyHJt.jpg&h=4409012d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lm0o4WR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLm0o4WR.jpg&h=c000c698&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PSHF7ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPSHF7ac.jpg&h=51349da6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/feoBFve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfeoBFve.jpg&h=6e89293a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aeCu0S7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaeCu0S7.jpg&h=331c8d94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f64c58a76cba11753acb5f1d462c9